('color-map', 'uk', 'Apparel', 'If the colour used to describe the product is nonstandard (e.g., sage), include the standard colour you wish to map to (e.g., green).  If no values are provided, customers will be unable to browse by colour.', 'Please see the Valid Values worksheet for the list of accepted values.', 'green', ''),
