('ProductName', 'de', 'Sport & Freizeit', 'Ein Kurztitel für das Produkt. Der Titel wird fett formatiert auf der Produktseite und in der Titelleiste des Browserfensters angezeigt. Es ist eine gute Idee, den Hersteller hier mit anzugeben. Wenn Sie zu einem Produkt Varianten anbieten, sollten sich diese auch im Titel unterscheiden (geben Sie z.B. die Farbe an).\n\nBitte lesen Sie den Styleguide, um mehr Informationen über die korrekte Defintion des Produktnamens zu erhalten.', 'Eine alphanumerische Zeichenfolge. Minimale Länge ist 1 Zeichen, maximale Länge: 100 Zeichen. Anmerkung: Hohe ASCII-Zeichen Typ 1 (®, ©, ™ usw.) oder andere Sonderzeichen werden nicht unterstützt. Keine HTML Tags oder Zeilenumbrüche verwenden.', 'Cube Mountainbike Acid 2010 schwarz/grau', 'Erforderlich'),
('ProductName', 'uk', 'Home and Garden', 'A short title for the product. This will be displayed in bold on the product page and in the title bar of the browser window.  If listing child products, please ensure to include the colour and &gt; or size in the product''s name to differentiate items.', 'An alphanumeric string; 1 character minimum in length and 100 characters maximum in length. Note: Type 1 High ASCII characters (®, ©, ™, etc.) or other special characters are not supported.', 'Men''s Polo Shirt, White, XL', 'Required'),
('ProductName', 'uk', 'Jewellery', 'A short title for the product. This will be displayed in bold on the product page and in the title bar of the browser window.  If listing child products, please ensure to include the colour and &gt; or size in the product''s name to differentiate items. Expected naming convention for Jewellery products will follow : Brand &gt; metal &gt; stone size or weight &gt; stone type  &gt; style &gt; product e.g Cartier 9ct Yellow Gold 1 &gt; 2 ct Diamond Eternity Ring\n\n***** Please note that either [StandardProductId & ProductIDType & ProductName] OR [Manufacturer & MfrModelNumber & ProductName] are required. ', 'An alphanumeric string; 1 character minimum in length and 100 characters maximum in length. Note: Type 1 High ASCII characters (®, ©, ™, etc.) or other special characters are not supported. ', 'Men''s Polo Shirt, White, XL', ''),
('ProductName', 'uk', 'Lighting', 'A short title for the product. This will be displayed in bold on the product page and in the title bar of the browser window. \n\nThe title must follow the structure [Brand] [Item Category] [Model Name &gt; Number] [Variation Information].\n\nWhen listing variation child products, please ensure to include the variation information like e.g. colour in the product''s name to differentiate items.', 'An alphanumeric string; 1 character minimum in length and 100 characters maximum in length. \n\nNote: Type 1 High ASCII characters (®, ©, ™, etc.) or other special characters are not supported.', 'Philips Energy Saving Lightbulb 11w BC Cap Stick 5 Pack', 'Required'),
('ProductName', 'uk', 'Sports', 'A short title for the product. This will be displayed in bold on the product page and in the title bar of the browser window.  If listing child products, please ensure to include the variation parameters (e.g., color and &gt; or size) in the product''s name to differentiate items.', 'An alphanumeric string; 1 character minimum in length and 100 characters maximum in length. Note: Type 1 High ASCII characters (®, ©, ™, etc.) or other special characters are not supported.', 'Junior Life Jacket, Orange, Medium', 'Required'),
('ProductName', 'uk', 'Watches', 'A short title for the product.  The title should include the product code and brand name.  This will be displayed in bold on the product page and in the title bar of the browser window.  If listing child products, please ensure to include the colour and &gt; or size in the product''s name to differentiate items.\n\n***Please note that [StandardProductID & ProductIDType & ProductName & Manufacturer & MfrPartNumber] are required.', 'An alphanumeric string; 1 character minimum in length and 100 characters maximum in length. Note: Type 1 High ASCII characters (®, ©, ™, etc.) or other special characters are not supported.', 'Men''s Polo Shirt, White, XL', 'Required'),
('ProductTaxCode', 'com', 'Home and Garden', 'Amazon.com''s standard code to identify the tax properties of a product.  ', 'Enter the product tax code supplied to you by Amazon.com.  If no entry is provided, the default is "A_GEN_NOTAX".', 'A_GEN_NOTAX', 'Optional'),
